# bin/

Central command router and command implementations for Intent CLI. Contains the main entry point, configuration management utilities, and specialized handlers for project initialization, steel thread management, diagnostics, and third-party integrations.

## Files

- `intent` -- Main CLI entry point and command router; dispatches to subcommands and plugins
- `intent_config` -- Shared configuration library for JSON parsing and project detection
- `intent_helpers` -- Utility functions for version management and YAML-to-JSON conversion
- `intent_bootstrap` -- First-time setup for Intent installations
- `intent_init` -- Initialize new Intent projects with directory structure and configuration
- `intent_doctor` -- Diagnose and fix configuration issues
- `intent_upgrade` -- Migrate existing STP projects to Intent v2.4.0
- `intent_info` -- Display installation status and project information
- `intent_help` -- Help system and command reference documentation
- `intent_st` -- Steel thread lifecycle management (new, list, show, edit, repair, sync)
- `intent_treeindex` -- Generate `.treeindex` directory summaries using Claude AI
- `intent_fileindex` -- Create and manage file indexes with checkbox state tracking
- `intent_backlog` -- Wrapper for Backlog.md task management integration
- `intent_bl` -- Shorthand alias for backlog commands
- `intent_task` -- Create and manage tasks linked to steel threads
- `intent_status` -- Sync steel thread status with Backlog task completion
- `intent_migrate` -- Migrate embedded tasks from steel threads to Backlog.md
- `intent_llm` -- LLM utilities for usage rules and context management
- `intent_organise` -- Organize steel threads into status directories
- `intent_main` -- Backward compatibility wrapper (stp alias)
- `intent_minimal` -- Minimal CLI wrapper for early testing phases
